title: Angel and the Badman
description:
Produced by and starring John Wayne ANGEL AND THE BADMAN is a film that many John Wayne fans may not have seen, nonetheless it&#039;s one of his best.

 Quirt Evens (John Wayne)an all round bad guy is nursed back to health and sought after by Penelope Worth (Gail Russell) a young Quaker. He eventually finds himself having to choose between his world of violence and Penelope.
